*gtoaster-1.0_beta6 (06 Sep 2002)

  30 Oct 2002; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org> gtoaster-1.0_beta6.ebuild,
  files/scdtosr.diff :
  Modified source code so detection of devices defaults to sr instead of
  scd.

  28 Oct 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  gtoaster-1.0_beta6.ebuild :
  Added app-cdr/cdrdao to DEPEND list, closing bug #9661 by
  grant.likely@gdcanada.com (Grant Likely)

  06 Sep 2002; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org>
  gtoaster-1.0_beta6.ebuild, files/digest-gtoaster-1.0_beta6 :
  Version bump.  nls additions.  recorder detection bug fix.  Burns
  faster than 24x are now possible.


*gtoaster-1.0_beta5 (28 Mar 2002)

